snippet: The man, who apparently committed suicide after escaping from the site of the shooting, had no known links to terrorist groups, officials said....
abstract: Swiss police find gunman who wounded three people at Islamic center in Zurich dead from apparent suicide; say he was Swiss citizen of Ghanaian descent with no known ties to terror groups.

byline.original: By NICK CUMMING-BRUCE and JACK EWING
byline.contributor: Nick Cumming-Bruce reported from Zurich, and Jack Ewing from Frankfurt.

lead_paragraph: The man, who apparently committed suicide after escaping from the site of the shooting, had no known links to terrorist groups, officials said.

headline.main: Gunman Who Shot 3 at Zurich Islamic Center Is Found Dead, Police Say
headline.print_headline: Gunman in Zurich Had No Ties to Terror Groups
